## ğŸ† Challenge: Factorial

```elixir
defmodule Factorial do
  def calc(0), do: 1
  def calc(n), do: n * calc(n - 1)
end

Factorial.calc(5)  # 5 * 4 * 3 * 2 * 1 = 120
```

